
'''柯邦迪'''（{{lang-pt|José Maria da Ponte e Horta}}，{{bd|1824年||1892年||}}），或譯「柯打」<ref name="macaudata-690">{{Cite web |url=http://www.macaudata.com/macaubook/encyclopedia/documents/690.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160105174841/http://www.macaudata.com/macaubook/encyclopedia/documents/690.htm |archive-date=2016-01-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、「邦迪‧柯打」<ref>{{harvnb|潮人物雜誌|2014|p=47}}[https://books.google.com/books?id=KharBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA47&lpg=PA47&dq=%E9%82%A6%E8%BF%AA%E2%80%A7%E6%9F%AF%E6%89%93&source=bl&ots=6Ielu1cZRs&sig=kvpjSN26NWmZ1AwhGCGlli0luqo&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiGicDuhv7JAhUin6YKHSOHCg0Q6AEIKTAC#v=onepage&q=%E9%82%A6%E8%BF%AA%E2%80%A7%E6%9F%AF%E6%89%93&f=false gUrl] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=KharBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA47&lpg=PA47&dq=%E9%82%A6%E8%BF%AA%E2%80%A7%E6%9F%AF%E6%89%93&source=bl&ots=6Ielu1cZRs&sig=kvpjSN26NWmZ1AwhGCGlli0luqo&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiGicDuhv7JAhUin6YKHSOHCg0Q6AEIKTAC#v=onepage&q=%E9%82%A6%E8%BF%AA%E2%80%A7%E6%9F%AF%E6%89%93&f=false |date=20160618014108 }}</ref><ref name="macaostreets-17-3387">https://macaostreets.iacm.gov.mo/s/route/detail.aspx?gid=17&id=3387f561-c04b-46e8-988d-de3e5c1bb3a4 {{Wayback|url=https://macaostreets.iacm.gov.mo/s/route/detail.aspx?gid=17&id=3387f561-c04b-46e8-988d-de3e5c1bb3a4 |date=20160107061320 }} [[柯邦迪前地|柯邦迪前地]]，更新日期：31/08/2015</ref>，[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]軍官。

柯邦迪出生在葡萄牙貴族家庭。曾加入葡萄牙軍隊，後成為Escola Politécnica de Lisboa的教授。

1866年10月26日，柯邦迪被任命為[[澳門|澳門]]總督{{r|macaudata-690}}，直到1868年8月3日離任。1870年至1873年期間，擔任[[安哥拉|安哥拉]]總督。<ref>[http://www.rulers.org/rula2.html#angola Rulers.org - Angola] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rulers.org/rula2.html#angola |date=20151214180324 }} {{vc|time=2015-12-27}}</ref><ref>[http://www.worldstatesmen.org/Angola.html worldstatesmen.org - Angola] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/65PGeP9Uz?url=http://www.worldstatesmen.org/Angola.html |date=20120212215927 |dateformat=iso }} {{vc|time=2015-12-27}}</ref><ref>African States and Rulers, John Stewart, McFarland</ref><ref name="dererummundi.blogspot">{{cite web |url=http://dererummundi.blogspot.hk/2009/02/uma-polemica-cientifica-oitocentista.html |title=Uma história da ciência portuguesa do século XIX contada por A. José Leonardo: |last1=José Leonardo |first1=A. |last2= |first2= |date= |language=pt |publisher=De Rerum Natura |accessdate=14 March 2013 |archive-date=2017-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170820035531/http://dererummundi.blogspot.hk/2009/02/uma-polemica-cientifica-oitocentista.html |dead-url=no }}{{vc|time=2015-12-27}}</ref>也有許多資料稱他曾擔任過[[佛得角|佛得角]]總督，但并沒有文獻能夠證明這一點。<ref name="dererummundi.blogspot" />

柯邦迪在1892年逝世，今日澳門有不少街道和建築物以他的名字命名，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://macauantigo.blogspot.com/2013/10/jose-maria-da-ponte-e-horta-1824-1892.html?_sm_au_=iHV7VDfVQWRqtVQQ |title=Macau Antiguo |last1=Botas |first1=João |language=pt |first2= |date=7 October 2013 |website=Macau Antiguo |publisher=Blogspot |access-date=24 March 2015 |archive-date=2017-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170820035032/http://macauantigo.blogspot.com/2013/10/jose-maria-da-ponte-e-horta-1824-1892.html?_sm_au_=iHV7VDfVQWRqtVQQ |dead-url=no }}{{vc|time=2015-12-27}}</ref>例如「[[柯邦迪前地|柯邦迪前地]]」{{r|macaostreets-17-3387}}。

